#

Classic Caesar Salad with Grilled Chicken

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SaladLight MealQuickHealthy

Description

A crisp and refreshing salad topped with grilled chicken, creamy dressing, and savory cheese, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • romaine lettuce: 1 large head
  • grilled chicken breast: 1
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup, shaved
  • croutons: 1 cup
  • caesar dressing: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
